snippet.title: Beter With A Friend - Teaser
snippet.description:
A little teaser for my collection of mini games for the Steam Deck: Better With A Friend. Games you can only play with somebody else. 

You can wishlist the game already on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2943100/Better_With_A_Friend/

#steamdeck #betterwithafriend #game #teaser
